HEADWORD: Newness
<hw>New"ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state
of being new; <as>as, the <ex>newness</ex> of a system; the
<ex>newness</ex> of a scene; <ex>newness</ex> of life.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

